
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

$ : wget https://storage.googleapis.com/flutter_infra_release/releases/stable/linux/flutter_linux_3.7.7-stable.tar.xz

$ : tar -xvf flutter_linux_3.7.7-stable.tar.xz

$ : echo 'export PATH="$PATH:$HOME/Repositorios/flutter/bin"' >> .bashrc

$ : source .bashrc

$ : flutter upgrade

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

$ : sudo apt-get install clang cmake ninja-build pkg-config libgtk-3-dev liblzma-dev

